1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:20,000
(Watch on www.dramacool.club Support Admin)

2
00:00:21,230 --> 00:00:23,670
[Government]

3
00:00:25,370 --> 00:00:29,270
[Government]

4
00:00:31,320 --> 00:00:33,030
How did you end up like this?

5
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:38,520
It was a twist of fate.

6
00:00:39,350 --> 00:00:40,880
Who could have foreseen it?

7
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,390
But I have my duties.

8
00:00:45,750 --> 00:00:46,950
I already did my best.

9
00:00:49,350 --> 00:00:51,010
As the Discipline Inspector,

10
00:00:52,350 --> 00:00:54,560
you are responsible
for supervising the army.

11
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:56,110
The rebel Sui Yuanhuai

12
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:58,000
has escaped repeatedly,

13
00:00:58,640 --> 00:01:00,440
and you cannot escape the blame.

14
00:01:01,710 --> 00:01:03,310
It was indeed my negligence.

15
00:01:04,150 --> 00:01:07,000
I have already reported it to His Majesty

16
00:01:07,870 --> 00:01:09,800
and am ready to accept punishment.

17
00:01:18,789 --> 00:01:20,990
You have followed General He for years.

18
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,200
You must have heard of

19
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:24,510
Li Bai's poem,
"Fighting South of the Wall."

20
00:01:24,510 --> 00:01:26,000
"Soldiers lie wasted in the wilderness;

21
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:28,260
the General's deeds amount to nothing."

22
00:01:28,310 --> 00:01:30,430
For the sake of so-called legitimacy,

23
00:01:30,430 --> 00:01:32,750
sacrificing countless innocent lives
in vain

24
00:01:32,750 --> 00:01:33,680
is cruel.

25
00:01:34,590 --> 00:01:36,150
You speak of negligence,

26
00:01:36,150 --> 00:01:38,680
but do you know
how many soldiers' efforts were wasted,

27
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,610
and how many people are suffering?

28
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:43,350
I am truly ashamed.

29
00:01:47,950 --> 00:01:50,150
As the eldest grandson of the Li family,

30
00:01:50,870 --> 00:01:52,039
this eternal infamy

31
00:01:53,229 --> 00:01:54,690
shall be borne by me alone.

32
00:01:54,979 --> 00:02:04,630
[Government]

33
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:00,160
The futile war you provoked,

34
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:03,350
and the soldiers who died unjustly...

35
00:02:03,350 --> 00:02:05,080
Can you bear the weight of that?

36
00:02:06,950 --> 00:02:07,790
Lord Li,

37
00:02:09,139 --> 00:02:10,800
let me remind you of one thing:

38
00:02:11,430 --> 00:02:14,760
do not forget why you entered the service
in the first place.

39
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,820
What did the Marquis of Wu'an say?

40
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,960
Xie Zheng...

41
00:02:37,750 --> 00:02:39,350
probably knows everything.

42
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:12,010
[Pursuit of Jade]

43
00:04:12,090 --> 00:04:14,710
[Episode 33]

44
00:04:14,730 --> 00:04:21,420
[Sesame Seed Bun]

45
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:23,600
What sin did the Liu family commit?

46
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:29,100
[Wanted] [Notice]

47
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:26,080
Their entire household was slaughtered.

48
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:28,310
Bandits are ruthless.

49
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:30,800
The massacre of the Liu family is nothing.

50
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,800
All of Lin'an Town was slaughtered.

51
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:36,530
No wonder the Marquis
wants to wipe out Qingfeng Stronghold.

52
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:38,540
[Wanted] [Notice]

53
00:04:37,430 --> 00:04:39,560
He is truly ridding the people of evil.

54
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,290
Indeed.

55
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:43,159
Look at this young lady.
She looks so graceful.

56
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:44,800
And yet she's a female bandit,

57
00:04:43,790 --> 00:04:46,250
[Sesame Seed Bun]

58
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,510
the Chief Master of Qingfeng Stronghold?

59
00:04:46,510 --> 00:04:47,480
Give me five flatbreads.

60
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,270
Okay.

61
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:48,950
Pah!

62
00:04:49,340 --> 00:04:49,800
Here.

63
00:04:59,070 --> 00:05:00,530
Watch where you're going.

64
00:05:31,710 --> 00:05:33,159
Sui Yuanqing...

65
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,860
You heartless thing.

66
00:05:39,870 --> 00:05:41,650
Where the hell are you?

67
00:05:44,630 --> 00:05:46,710
The government dogs are after me,

68
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:49,750
and the bandits want me too.

69
00:05:50,550 --> 00:05:52,390
Even the 13 lives of the Liu family

70
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:54,000
are pinned on me.

71
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,659
Now I am

72
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:59,680
being chased like a stray dog.

73
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,480
But you—

74
00:06:01,430 --> 00:06:02,960
You are nowhere to be found.

75
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:32,040
Isn't that the official from Lin'an Town?

76
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,240
What is he doing here?

77
00:07:06,130 --> 00:07:09,800
[Majestic and Efficacious]

78
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:18,840
Your Highness,
have some hot tea to warm yourself.

79
00:07:22,310 --> 00:07:24,040
We are not far from the Capital.

80
00:07:24,510 --> 00:07:27,510
Once we reach the Capital,
Your Highness will be safe.

81
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:30,720
Qi Min!

82
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:32,920
Get the hell out here!

83
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,480
Not again.

84
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,870
His nose is sharper than a dog's.

85
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:45,800
He really wouldn't leave us alone.

86
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:29,550
I'm going to kill you, you bastard,

87
00:08:29,830 --> 00:08:32,960
and send you to hell
to be with Father and Mother Consort.

88
00:08:33,549 --> 00:08:34,789
Living under someone else's name

89
00:08:34,789 --> 00:08:37,250
and living a stolen life
for over 10 years...

90
00:08:38,390 --> 00:08:40,600
I assume you have no last words.

91
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,240
My brother, Yuanqing...

92
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:47,500
You're not worthy of calling me that!

93
00:08:58,750 --> 00:08:59,510
Yuanqing.

94
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,810
If you're angry with me,

95
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,670
I apologize.

96
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,440
Believe it or not,

97
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:09,410
I never intended to hurt you at all.

98
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,750
Never intended to hurt me?

99
00:09:15,210 --> 00:09:17,000
Then what about Mother Consort?

100
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,750
How did she ever wrong you?

101
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,000
Tell me.

102
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,840
Tell me!

103
00:09:44,870 --> 00:09:46,390
Is this what you meant by

104
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,440
never intending to hurt me?

105
00:09:52,790 --> 00:09:53,550
Yuanqing.

106
00:09:54,630 --> 00:09:56,000
I warned you long ago.

107
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,360
Don't be too arrogant.

108
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:02,260
Now I can give you
the second half of that advice.

109
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:06,440
You will die a violent death.

110
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,120
I was so stupid.

111
00:10:24,870 --> 00:10:27,130
I always treated you like my own brother.

112
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:30,330
I couldn't even bring myself
to kill you just now.

113
00:10:34,930 --> 00:10:37,430
You and your family owe me this!

114
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:41,090
Everyone in Lord Changxin's household
deserves to die!

115
00:10:43,580 --> 00:10:46,030
Why is it that
you are healthy and look energetic,

116
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:48,000
while I look like a wretched ghost?

117
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,840
Why can you practice martial arts,

118
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,720
ride horses, and shoot arrows,

119
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:56,080
while I am plagued by chronic illness
and have to drink medicine every day?

120
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:57,600
The pain in my heart

121
00:10:57,910 --> 00:10:59,360
and the wounds on my body

122
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:02,910
were caused by Lord Changxin and Wei Yan!

123
00:11:03,630 --> 00:11:05,430
My father and mother consort...

124
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:08,150
I must avenge them.

125
00:11:08,510 --> 00:11:11,790
None of you will die a peaceful death!

126
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:18,390
You sound so righteous.

127
00:11:20,170 --> 00:11:22,770
But my mother never mistreated you.

128
00:11:23,650 --> 00:11:26,510
On the contrary,
the Crown Princess killed her son.

129
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:29,320
My mother raised you for over a decade,

130
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,840
and you took over the mansion.

131
00:11:32,550 --> 00:11:35,550
How could you bring yourself to harm her?

132
00:11:38,910 --> 00:11:41,120
Because my heart died long ago.

133
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:44,720
Of course I could do it.

134
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:53,040
Your Highness, we have to go!
We cannot stay here for long.

135
00:12:25,630 --> 00:12:26,710
Sui Yuanqing.

136
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,120
You forgot

137
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,870
what I taught you.

138
00:12:32,870 --> 00:12:34,840
Those who are soft-hearted

139
00:12:36,550 --> 00:12:39,600
are not fit to stand on this battlefield,

140
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,670
let alone dream

141
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:45,270
of ruling this world.

142
00:12:54,390 --> 00:12:56,500
[To Know Others is Wisdom]

143
00:14:06,270 --> 00:14:07,130
Your Highness.

144
00:14:07,270 --> 00:14:08,000
I am late.

145
00:14:10,590 --> 00:14:12,720
You might as well show up when I'm dead.

146
00:14:14,790 --> 00:14:16,750
It was your Li family who sent word to me,

147
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:18,480
saying everything was arranged.

148
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:21,410
But what was waiting for me
throughout this journey?

149
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:23,630
Xie Zheng's personal guards,

150
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:26,510
and that madman, Sui Yuanqing.

151
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:29,990
That was indeed my fault.

152
00:14:30,870 --> 00:14:32,730
Please punish me, Your Highness.

153
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:36,080
I know you dislike me.

154
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:38,720
Protecting and saving me

155
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:41,600
is merely obeying
your grandfather's orders.

156
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:44,080
Since you have decided to join us,

157
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:46,300
there is absolutely no turning back.

158
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:49,570
Only by escorting me safely to the Capital

159
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:52,610
will your Li family
stand a chance of winning,

160
00:14:52,670 --> 00:14:55,070
and your years of planning
won't be in vain.

161
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:58,120
Otherwise,

162
00:14:58,600 --> 00:15:00,330
I will drag you all down with me.

163
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:03,370
Not only will the entire Li clan
be destroyed,

164
00:15:03,790 --> 00:15:06,520
but Wei Yan will also remain in power
for decades,

165
00:15:06,870 --> 00:15:08,800
with the common people suffering.

166
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:16,120
I heard you care for the people.

167
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:20,820
You wouldn't want to see
the chaos of war rise again, would you?

168
00:15:23,030 --> 00:15:23,720
I...

169
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,480
will do my best.

170
00:15:28,630 --> 00:15:29,320
Also,

171
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:32,240
I don't care what method you use,

172
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,670
kill Yu Bao'er for me.

173
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:37,440
Bring Yu Qianqian back unharmed.

174
00:15:37,860 --> 00:15:41,620
[Majestic and Efficacious]

175
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:39,610
Your Highness.

176
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:43,490
I heard Yu Bao'er
is your only flesh and blood.

177
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:45,600
I do not acknowledge him.

178
00:15:45,670 --> 00:15:47,800
This bloodline will be the death of me.

179
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,120
A worthless life

180
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:52,390
compared to the entire Li clan—

181
00:15:52,390 --> 00:15:55,320
you should know which weighs heavier.

182
00:16:15,570 --> 00:16:20,120
[Merciful White Dragon Temple]

183
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:19,120
If you cannot find the person I seek,

184
00:16:19,510 --> 00:16:21,270
my alliance with your Li clan

185
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:22,910
ends here.

186
00:16:32,430 --> 00:16:33,960
Disregarding
the kindness of his upbringing,

187
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,360
killing his brother,

188
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:37,210
and hunting down his own child.

189
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:40,570
How can a heartless and unjust man
like him

190
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:42,240
be Emperor?

191
00:16:44,790 --> 00:16:46,190
If he ascends the throne,

192
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:48,820
he will surely not be a wise ruler.

193
00:16:51,550 --> 00:16:52,360
Grandfather,

194
00:16:53,770 --> 00:16:55,140
you are truly wrong.

195
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:43,960
You're not dead yet?

196
00:17:50,030 --> 00:17:51,000
Kill me

197
00:17:52,690 --> 00:17:54,290
to avenge yourself.

198
00:17:58,070 --> 00:17:59,400
All right.

199
00:18:03,950 --> 00:18:05,110
Sui Yuanqing.

200
00:18:07,580 --> 00:18:08,780
Then before you die,

201
00:18:12,270 --> 00:18:14,200
there's something I'd like to ask.

202
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:20,260
Have you ever really liked me?

203
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:31,700
I, Sui Yuanqing, throughout my life,

204
00:18:32,350 --> 00:18:34,210
have deceived countless people.

205
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:37,920
Now that I'm about to die,

206
00:18:40,070 --> 00:18:41,270
logically speaking,

207
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,750
I should spin some lies

208
00:18:45,700 --> 00:18:47,500
to make you risk your life for me.

209
00:18:49,590 --> 00:18:51,510
But it's really strange.

210
00:18:54,920 --> 00:18:57,440
I don't want to lie
to you at all right now.

211
00:19:01,820 --> 00:19:02,970
I've never

212
00:19:05,270 --> 00:19:07,610
truly liked you.

213
00:19:17,270 --> 00:19:18,900
Look at yourself.

214
00:19:20,880 --> 00:19:22,360
It's best you never did.

215
00:19:30,510 --> 00:19:31,900
Without you,

216
00:19:34,830 --> 00:19:36,480
my life ahead

217
00:19:39,310 --> 00:19:41,200
will be incredibly carefree.

218
00:19:56,160 --> 00:19:58,110
If you can survive,

219
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:00,000
take this

220
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:03,110
and find Fan Changyu.

221
00:20:08,250 --> 00:20:09,270
What is this?

222
00:20:13,310 --> 00:20:15,310
You were together before after all.

223
00:20:16,350 --> 00:20:17,880
I'm leaving you a way out.

224
00:20:19,550 --> 00:20:22,830
Qi Min wants the whole world to suffer.

225
00:20:23,590 --> 00:20:24,920
I, Sui Yuanqing,

226
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:28,640
only want him to suffer alone.

227
00:20:30,240 --> 00:20:31,920
Why would she believe me?

228
00:20:56,550 --> 00:20:58,440
Then I will give you a

229
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:04,110
pledge of loyalty.

230
00:21:34,510 --> 00:21:36,210
Sui Yuanqing!

231
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:48,520
[Three days later]

232
00:21:47,920 --> 00:21:48,720
Your Majesty,

233
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:50,750
I have a matter to report.

234
00:21:51,070 --> 00:21:52,680
Wei Yan lacks discipline
over his subordinates.

235
00:21:52,680 --> 00:21:54,270
This act is tantamount to rebellion.

236
00:21:54,270 --> 00:21:56,070
It must be punished severely.

237
00:22:01,920 --> 00:22:04,550
Grand Tutor, you understand me.
Speak freely.

238
00:22:05,030 --> 00:22:05,830
Your Majesty.

239
00:22:06,110 --> 00:22:07,070
The Marquis of Wu'an

240
00:22:07,070 --> 00:22:09,480
is the nephew personally cultivated
by Prime Minister Wei.

241
00:22:09,480 --> 00:22:10,750
Yet, in front of the troops,

242
00:22:10,750 --> 00:22:14,350
he sliced off the ear of Eunuch Li,
who was delivering the decree.

243
00:22:14,350 --> 00:22:16,960
Such behavior is incredibly arrogant.

244
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:18,400
It is truly treasonous.

245
00:22:18,400 --> 00:22:21,260
By law, he should be executed
as a warning to others.

246
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:26,270
Grand Tutor Li speaks frankly.

247
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:30,330
Prime Minister Wei, what is your view?

248
00:22:30,830 --> 00:22:32,200
In my opinion...

249
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:34,350
This Eunuch Li

250
00:22:34,590 --> 00:22:38,560
kept claiming
the Marquis of Wu'an intended to rebel.

251
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:40,200
However, I believe

252
00:22:40,680 --> 00:22:44,000
the Marquis
merely lost control in his anger.

253
00:22:45,270 --> 00:22:46,350
After all, in this world,

254
00:22:46,350 --> 00:22:49,310
not everyone can be a modest gentleman

255
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:52,440
like Grand Tutor Li's grandson,
Discipline Inspector Li.

256
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:54,850
Even if Your Majesty
suddenly changed your mind

257
00:22:54,850 --> 00:22:57,400
about marrying the Princess Royal
to someone else,

258
00:22:57,400 --> 00:23:00,200
he could accept it gladly.

259
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:07,970
What Prime Minister Wei said is also true.

260
00:23:09,000 --> 00:23:10,550
Military commanders

261
00:23:10,790 --> 00:23:13,270
are rough men.

262
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:20,330
Prime Minister Wei!

263
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:23,030
He Jingyuan's control over half the army

264
00:23:23,030 --> 00:23:25,480
has fallen into the hands
of a mere village girl.

265
00:23:25,480 --> 00:23:29,440
That Commandant Fan cannot even
read military maps or treatises,

266
00:23:29,440 --> 00:23:31,440
yet because of your selfish motives,

267
00:23:31,440 --> 00:23:33,720
she became an Army Supervisor
in Jizhou Prefecture.

268
00:23:33,720 --> 00:23:35,680
The Command Office is in chaos.

269
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:38,340
May I ask,
where is the military discipline?

270
00:23:38,350 --> 00:23:40,080
And where is the law of the land?

271
00:23:40,110 --> 00:23:41,540
Is that so?

272
00:23:44,940 --> 00:23:45,740
Your Majesty!

273
00:23:45,880 --> 00:23:47,750
The Marquis of Wu'an and Commandant Fan

274
00:23:47,750 --> 00:23:49,550
have both made
distinguished military contributions.

275
00:23:49,550 --> 00:23:50,960
But rewards and punishments
should be clearly distinct—

276
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:52,550
they cannot be conflated.

277
00:23:52,550 --> 00:23:54,720
What do you think, Your Majesty?

278
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:58,960
Report!

279
00:24:00,310 --> 00:24:01,110
Your Majesty.

280
00:24:01,310 --> 00:24:03,770
This is an 800-li urgent report
from Jizhou.

281
00:24:03,790 --> 00:24:04,440
Present it at once.

282
00:24:04,440 --> 00:24:05,070
Yes.

283
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:15,110
Excellent!

284
00:24:15,920 --> 00:24:18,480
The Marquis of Wu'an and Commandant Fan
have joined forces.

285
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:20,810
The rebel Sui Yuanhuai has been executed.

286
00:24:20,830 --> 00:24:23,350
Lord Changxin and his two sons
are all dead.

287
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:25,070
The Sui family line is severed.

288
00:24:25,070 --> 00:24:27,720
From now on, there are no more
Chongzhou rebels in this world.

289
00:24:27,720 --> 00:24:28,250
Perfect!

290
00:24:33,920 --> 00:24:38,320
A perfect harmony between General
and Minister defeating the enemy together.

291
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:40,940
This is my great fortune.

292
00:24:41,070 --> 00:24:43,240
And a blessing for the Great Yin.

293
00:24:46,790 --> 00:24:51,200
Worldly affairs are like chess;
every game is new.

294
00:24:51,830 --> 00:24:55,550
Since the Marquis of Wu'an and Commandant Fan
have achieved consecutive victories,

295
00:24:55,550 --> 00:24:57,350
I shall reward them.

296
00:24:57,510 --> 00:24:59,310
I shall reward them generously.

297
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:01,000
Your Majesty is wise.

298
00:25:03,900 --> 00:25:05,200
Your Majesty is wise.

299
00:25:07,190 --> 00:25:10,240
[Government]

300
00:25:10,340 --> 00:25:18,340
[Peace at the border]

301
00:25:22,440 --> 00:25:22,960
My Lord.

302
00:25:23,490 --> 00:25:25,830
The Princess Royal
is about to return to the capital.

303
00:25:25,830 --> 00:25:28,790
Commandant Fan is holding
a farewell banquet for her tonight.

304
00:25:28,790 --> 00:25:29,790
Will you be going?

305
00:25:47,120 --> 00:25:47,810
Also,

306
00:25:48,140 --> 00:25:48,880
tomorrow morning,

307
00:25:48,880 --> 00:25:52,610
the Marquis is sending massed troops
to escort the Princess Royal.

308
00:26:06,640 --> 00:26:08,240
I am too ashamed to face them.

309
00:26:21,550 --> 00:26:22,880
Come on, come on.

310
00:26:22,880 --> 00:26:24,480
Come on.

311
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:36,140
Here.

312
00:26:36,170 --> 00:26:37,020
Here.

313
00:26:38,040 --> 00:26:40,210
[Qinwen Hall]

314
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:44,720
Come on.

315
00:26:44,740 --> 00:26:45,680
-Ten.
-Twenty.

316
00:26:53,270 --> 00:26:55,590
It's getting messy with all the drinking.

317
00:26:55,590 --> 00:26:58,120
Why hasn't
Discipline Inspector Li come yet?

318
00:26:58,790 --> 00:27:00,240
He caught a cold.

319
00:27:00,510 --> 00:27:02,040
He probably cannot make it.

320
00:27:04,550 --> 00:27:05,240
Everyone.

321
00:27:06,450 --> 00:27:07,790
I cannot hold my liquor well.

322
00:27:07,790 --> 00:27:09,720
I will take my leave after this cup.

323
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:26,210
Farewell, Your Highness.

324
00:27:36,830 --> 00:27:37,530
Sit.

325
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:45,270
The Princess Royal
returns to the palace tomorrow.

326
00:27:45,270 --> 00:27:47,920
If anyone has anything to say,

327
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:49,560
do not let tonight slip away.

328
00:27:51,510 --> 00:27:52,030
I'll go.

329
00:27:51,960 --> 00:27:54,000
[Qinwen Hall]

330
00:27:52,030 --> 00:27:52,760
You sit down!

331
00:27:52,880 --> 00:27:53,510
All right.

332
00:27:57,400 --> 00:27:58,640
Go on!

333
00:28:00,790 --> 00:28:02,120
What does he have to say?

334
00:28:03,350 --> 00:28:04,340
Will he go?

335
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:05,240
H-He's going.

336
00:28:06,350 --> 00:28:07,210
Your Highness!

337
00:28:07,510 --> 00:28:09,110
Your Highness, please wait!

338
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:10,640
Your Highness.

339
00:28:10,640 --> 00:28:11,790
The Princess Royal
doesn't want to see you.

340
00:28:11,790 --> 00:28:12,750
I just want to ask a few questions.

341
00:28:12,750 --> 00:28:13,440
Go away!

342
00:28:15,270 --> 00:28:16,160
I imagine Your Highness wouldn't want

343
00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:19,690
to return to the palace
with regrets and unanswered questions.

344
00:28:25,190 --> 00:28:26,250
Leave us, Jianjia.

345
00:28:34,270 --> 00:28:35,020
Allow me.

346
00:28:41,680 --> 00:28:42,540
Your Highness.

347
00:28:43,960 --> 00:28:45,200
I actually want to ask,

348
00:28:45,200 --> 00:28:47,730
why are you
suddenly returning to the palace?

349
00:28:48,590 --> 00:28:51,120
I have been
in the Northwest for over 5 months.

350
00:28:51,790 --> 00:28:53,160
I feel exhausted.

351
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:56,900
I've also suddenly realized something—

352
00:28:57,350 --> 00:29:00,880
I don't want to waste any more time
on pointless entanglements.

353
00:29:01,550 --> 00:29:04,010
I assume you must be greatly relieved.

354
00:29:07,200 --> 00:29:09,400
Since Your Highness has realized this,

355
00:29:09,590 --> 00:29:12,190
I should naturally offer
my congratulations.

356
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:14,060
However, there are some words

357
00:29:14,960 --> 00:29:16,590
that I have kept hidden
in my heart for a long time

358
00:29:16,590 --> 00:29:18,790
that I wish to share
with Your Highness.

359
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:20,680
But my clan's rules are strict,

360
00:29:20,680 --> 00:29:22,610
and I dared not overstep my bounds.

361
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:25,590
So, a few days ago,

362
00:29:27,030 --> 00:29:28,230
I returned to Hejian.

363
00:29:29,880 --> 00:29:32,740
I knelt in the ancestral hall
for 3 days and 3 nights,

364
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:36,680
and finally obtained
the clan leader's forgiveness.

365
00:29:36,790 --> 00:29:37,930
Only then do I dare

366
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:41,060
to reveal my feelings to you here.

367
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,160
Go on.

368
00:29:48,050 --> 00:29:48,850
Fan!

369
00:29:51,270 --> 00:29:52,110
-I…
-Slowly.

370
00:29:52,510 --> 00:29:55,070
I have to have a few drinks
with you alone.

371
00:29:55,400 --> 00:29:57,130
Do you still... have wine here?

372
00:29:58,800 --> 00:30:00,800
I... Let me speak from the heart.

373
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:04,650
I, Jin, have never admired anyone.

374
00:30:04,790 --> 00:30:06,040
But I admire you.

375
00:30:06,830 --> 00:30:08,310
Before I met you,

376
00:30:08,750 --> 00:30:10,640
I never believed

377
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:13,720
that a woman
with such thin arms and legs like you

378
00:30:13,720 --> 00:30:15,490
could go on battlefields.

379
00:30:16,230 --> 00:30:18,480
Can this small body
of yours go on battlefields?

380
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:19,350
Never heard of it.

381
00:30:19,350 --> 00:30:20,310
Fan can.

382
00:30:20,400 --> 00:30:22,590
So I admire you.

383
00:30:22,590 --> 00:30:24,880
My boys all admire you.

384
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:25,340
Come on.

385
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:30,900
Come!

386
00:30:32,110 --> 00:30:33,590
-Cheers to Fan.
-Come on.

387
00:30:33,590 --> 00:30:34,480
-Come on.
-Come on.

388
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:35,270
Brothers!

389
00:30:35,310 --> 00:30:35,830
Pour the wine.

390
00:30:35,830 --> 00:30:36,640
Pour, pour.

391
00:30:37,350 --> 00:30:38,720
My wife can't hold her liquor well.

392
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:39,480
I'll drink for her.

393
00:30:39,480 --> 00:30:40,180
Here.

394
00:30:41,680 --> 00:30:43,340
What wife?

395
00:30:44,110 --> 00:30:46,200
She is the head of your family.

396
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:48,590
Everyone in Lin'an knows

397
00:30:48,770 --> 00:30:50,890
you are the matrilocal husband
of the Fan family.

398
00:30:50,890 --> 00:30:53,510
Once you married in, you have to listen
to the head of the house.

399
00:30:53,510 --> 00:30:54,200
Isn't that right?

400
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:54,790
Exactly.

401
00:30:54,790 --> 00:30:57,310
You usually dress like a gentleman.

402
00:30:57,310 --> 00:31:00,070
Yes, you're the Marquis of Wu'an.

403
00:31:00,350 --> 00:31:01,790
But you can't deny

404
00:31:01,790 --> 00:31:03,590
the marriage vows you took.

405
00:31:03,590 --> 00:31:04,990
You can't just deny them.

406
00:31:06,880 --> 00:31:09,350
Forget about
this matrilocal husband nonsense.

407
00:31:09,350 --> 00:31:10,550
I can drink this wine.

408
00:31:24,000 --> 00:31:26,400
-I'm old. I don't remember what I said.
-Sit, sit.

409
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:27,550
I have a low tolerance for alcohol,

410
00:31:27,550 --> 00:31:29,350
so I didn't hold the cup steadily.

411
00:31:29,350 --> 00:31:31,350
My wife and I will take our leave now.

412
00:31:31,680 --> 00:31:32,830
Take your time drinking, everyone!

413
00:31:32,830 --> 00:31:33,590
Fan!

414
00:31:34,030 --> 00:31:34,720
Hey!

415
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:37,720
A hundred years ago,

416
00:31:37,720 --> 00:31:41,670
[Dingcang Pavilion]

417
00:31:38,590 --> 00:31:41,240
the Gongsun clan was once in its prime.

418
00:31:42,750 --> 00:31:45,480
All past Empresses
came from the Gongsun family.

419
00:31:47,240 --> 00:31:49,040
But a tall tree catches the wind.

420
00:31:49,390 --> 00:31:50,990
And they all met a tragic end.

421
00:31:51,720 --> 00:31:53,650
When the Great Ancestor was alive,

422
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:56,690
a dragon robe
was found in the Eastern Palace.

423
00:31:58,300 --> 00:32:01,030
Crown Prince Shaoyang
was demoted to a commoner.

424
00:32:02,510 --> 00:32:04,840
The two Empresses from the Gongsun family

425
00:32:05,070 --> 00:32:06,920
hanged themselves in the palace.

426
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:07,990
The Gongsun clan

427
00:32:08,830 --> 00:32:11,030
had their homes raided and were exiled.

428
00:32:12,790 --> 00:32:15,530
Even the plaque
at Luyuan Academy's Library

429
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:17,260
was nearly taken back.

430
00:32:18,960 --> 00:32:20,420
I know about this.

431
00:32:21,270 --> 00:32:22,440
The Gongsun case

432
00:32:23,270 --> 00:32:24,570
was eventually proven

433
00:32:25,790 --> 00:32:28,000
to be a frame-up by a prince.

434
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:32,430
In this world,

435
00:32:32,720 --> 00:32:35,250
there is no such thing
as a flawless frame-up.

436
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:38,160
It was just that the Emperor
on the throne back then

437
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:40,690
could no longer tolerate
the Gongsun family.

438
00:32:41,550 --> 00:32:43,010
The Gongsun branch family

439
00:32:43,360 --> 00:32:46,560
has struggled to survive at Luyuan Academy
for a century.

440
00:32:48,110 --> 00:32:50,400
The first rule set for the clan was:

441
00:32:51,350 --> 00:32:52,810
do not enter officialdom.

442
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:58,070
Actually,

443
00:32:59,670 --> 00:33:03,000
from the first day Your Highness arrived
at Luyuan Academy,

444
00:33:03,000 --> 00:33:04,480
I knew you were a woman.

445
00:33:06,170 --> 00:33:07,110
When you played

446
00:33:07,110 --> 00:33:09,710
that first game of chess
with me at the Library,

447
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:11,030
I already knew

448
00:33:12,590 --> 00:33:13,680
that the person
who broke my chess formation

449
00:33:13,680 --> 00:33:15,400
at Fengyu Pavilion was you.

450
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:18,550
However,

451
00:33:21,070 --> 00:33:23,400
when I found out
the girl I had long admired

452
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:27,090
was actually
the current Princess Royal,

453
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:29,430
I felt no joy in my heart.

454
00:33:32,070 --> 00:33:34,130
I only lamented how fate toys with me.

455
00:33:35,510 --> 00:33:37,720
Then why are you telling me

456
00:33:39,720 --> 00:33:40,830
this now?

457
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:53,610
I want to propose to Your Highness.

458
00:33:56,510 --> 00:33:57,200
I...

459
00:33:59,550 --> 00:34:01,350
have admired you for a long time.

460
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:04,070
Today, I boldly ask Your Highness:

461
00:34:05,260 --> 00:34:06,200
if one day,

462
00:34:07,310 --> 00:34:08,480
after I help Jiuheng

463
00:34:09,110 --> 00:34:11,110
bring down Wei Yan and the Li family,

464
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:14,530
would you, Princess Royal,

465
00:34:15,150 --> 00:34:17,070
be willing to live with me in Hejian

466
00:34:17,070 --> 00:34:18,590
as a carefree couple?

467
00:34:25,630 --> 00:34:26,960
You can rest assured.

468
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:29,230
The Gongsun family
has accumulated wealth for a century

469
00:34:29,230 --> 00:34:30,190
and still has some assets,

470
00:34:30,190 --> 00:34:31,449
I won't let you suffer.

471
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:35,090
-It's just that Hejian's no match to—
-What if I say no?

472
00:34:49,070 --> 00:34:49,929
In that case...

473
00:34:54,510 --> 00:34:55,880
I spoke out of turn.

474
00:34:57,280 --> 00:34:59,080
Please forgive my foolishness.

475
00:35:13,140 --> 00:35:14,390
Gongsun Blockhead.

476
00:35:17,350 --> 00:35:18,180
I

477
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:21,890
want the thousands of books
in your library

478
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:23,740
as the betrothal gift.

479
00:35:24,590 --> 00:35:25,590
Do you agree?

480
00:35:31,880 --> 00:35:33,010
You're hesitating?

481
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:39,020
Y-Yes.

482
00:35:39,110 --> 00:35:40,640
Yes. I agree to everything.

483
00:35:41,810 --> 00:35:44,400
My family has 12 library buildings.

484
00:35:45,280 --> 00:35:46,410
I wonder, Princess,

485
00:35:47,110 --> 00:35:48,440
which one do you want?

486
00:35:48,800 --> 00:35:49,800
I want them all!

487
00:35:52,450 --> 00:35:53,000
Okay.

488
00:35:55,510 --> 00:35:56,110
Okay.

489
00:36:02,110 --> 00:36:04,070
Don't pull me.

490
00:36:08,500 --> 00:36:10,460
Where are you taking me?

491
00:36:11,670 --> 00:36:13,590
You're drunk.
I'm taking you back to your room.

492
00:36:13,590 --> 00:36:14,120
Let's go.

493
00:36:14,280 --> 00:36:16,320
I'm not drunk, Your Lordship.

494
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:24,070
You can't change

495
00:36:25,560 --> 00:36:27,090
how you address me, can you?

496
00:36:30,630 --> 00:36:32,230
Except for "Your Lordship,"

497
00:36:32,750 --> 00:36:34,610
you can call me whatever you want.

498
00:36:37,360 --> 00:36:40,840
♪ In a lifetime of storms,
a fleeting bloom ♪

499
00:36:41,410 --> 00:36:44,010
♪ The most beautiful scenery
becomes a poem ♪

500
00:36:44,640 --> 00:36:48,020
♪ For a chance encounter ♪

501
00:36:49,200 --> 00:36:52,830
♪ A single letter of longing,
half a lifetime apart ♪

502
00:36:53,170 --> 00:36:55,410
♪ I'll burn out my passion for you ♪

503
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:56,230
Yan Zheng...

504
00:36:55,770 --> 00:36:59,280
♪ Just for a glance ♪

505
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:58,700
Your name is Yan Zheng.

506
00:36:59,580 --> 00:37:00,340
♪ In this life ♪

507
00:37:00,360 --> 00:37:02,950
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

508
00:37:02,970 --> 00:37:04,630
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

509
00:37:05,010 --> 00:37:05,860
♪ On this journey ♪

510
00:37:05,070 --> 00:37:06,070
Can I call you

511
00:37:05,890 --> 00:37:08,680
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

512
00:37:07,070 --> 00:37:09,280
Yan Zheng in the future?

513
00:37:08,700 --> 00:37:10,750
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

514
00:37:10,780 --> 00:37:11,630
♪ After we part ♪

515
00:37:11,650 --> 00:37:14,640
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

516
00:37:14,670 --> 00:37:16,980
♪ Just one thought makes me sick ♪

517
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:21,630
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

518
00:37:21,960 --> 00:37:25,360
♪ We'll never be apart ♪

519
00:37:22,430 --> 00:37:24,030
Your hand...

520
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:26,880
Does it hurt?

521
