Even though I can't read them.

553
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:03,540
I'll be going now.

554
00:39:04,220 --> 00:39:05,050
Safe travels.

555
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:28,490
I'm leaving.

556
00:39:55,030 --> 00:39:56,710
Since you can't bear to part with her,

557
00:39:56,710 --> 00:39:58,310
why not see her off yourself?

558
00:39:58,630 --> 00:39:59,880
If I went,

559
00:39:59,880 --> 00:40:01,680
I'm afraid I wouldn't let her go.

560
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:07,590
A move played cannot be taken back.

561
00:40:07,590 --> 00:40:09,450
What I promised you still stands.

562
00:40:10,230 --> 00:40:11,880
How am I the one holding you back

563
00:40:11,880 --> 00:40:13,210
and ruining your plans?

564
00:40:15,030 --> 00:40:16,810
We have already promised each other.

565
00:40:16,810 --> 00:40:17,930
Once this is over,

566
00:40:17,960 --> 00:40:19,630
we will return to Hejian together,

567
00:40:19,630 --> 00:40:22,320
find a quiet place,
and spend the rest of our lives in peace.

568
00:40:22,320 --> 00:40:24,150
The Capital is treacherous.

569
00:40:24,150 --> 00:40:26,080
It is indeed imperative to act now.

570
00:40:27,320 --> 00:40:29,180
It is time to return to the Capital

571
00:40:29,710 --> 00:40:31,320
and finish what needs to be done,

572
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:32,400
once and for all.

573
00:40:36,520 --> 00:40:42,250
[Capital]

574
00:40:48,900 --> 00:40:50,110
Not bad, not bad.

575
00:40:53,550 --> 00:40:54,780
Drink some more.

576
00:40:55,190 --> 00:40:56,070
I want to eat this.

577
00:40:56,070 --> 00:40:56,590
Here.

578
00:40:56,670 --> 00:40:57,230
Okay.

579
00:40:59,960 --> 00:41:00,920
Stop it.

580
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:02,320
Have another drink.

581
00:41:04,510 --> 00:41:05,480
Mr. Li?

582
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:11,330
I was wondering why I haven't seen
Ms. Yueli these past few days.

583
00:41:13,240 --> 00:41:17,100
Turns out someone is hogging
the Jingque Tower and refusing to leave.

584
00:41:23,110 --> 00:41:24,320
Wei!

585
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:27,740
Aren't you supposed
to be serving in the Northwest?

586
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:36,150
[Grand Tutor Li's grandson,
Li Huaixian]

587
00:41:30,480 --> 00:41:32,810
I heard the Marquis of Wu'an has returned.

588
00:41:34,070 --> 00:41:36,600
Did you step down
to make way for your betters?

589
00:41:45,230 --> 00:41:45,840
Get lost.

590
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:51,400
As expected, bastards

591
00:41:51,400 --> 00:41:53,660
are never as good as the biological ones.

592
00:41:55,670 --> 00:41:57,530
It seems that the Marquis of Wu'an

593
00:41:57,710 --> 00:42:00,170
is Prime Minister Wei's
own flesh and blood.

594
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:02,060
Everyone, get out.

595
00:42:03,480 --> 00:42:04,190
Yes, Sir.

596
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:20,920
Say that again.

597
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:23,130
Why play dumb?

598
00:42:23,400 --> 00:42:25,460
Word has spread all over the Capital.

599
00:42:25,550 --> 00:42:28,150
The Prime Minister
and his wife are estranged.

600
00:42:28,780 --> 00:42:31,180
You are not Prime Minister Wei's son
at all.

601
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:37,480
Wei Xuan!

602
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:38,210
How dare you!

603
00:42:40,650 --> 00:42:42,090
You're just a bastard.

604
00:42:42,660 --> 00:42:45,670
Lying to people all day
using Prime Minister Wei's name.

605
00:42:45,670 --> 00:42:47,000
Your mother is nothing!

606
00:42:47,320 --> 00:42:48,670
I've long heard
that the Prime Minister's true love

607
00:42:48,670 --> 00:42:51,670
is his childhood sweetheart
from the palace, Lady Qi.

608
00:42:53,320 --> 00:42:54,540
Li...

609
00:42:55,070 --> 00:42:56,620
You're full of crap!

610
00:42:56,840 --> 00:42:57,840
If we were on the battlefield,

611
00:42:57,840 --> 00:42:59,640
I would have killed you already.

612
00:43:00,590 --> 00:43:02,190
I'll give you one chance.

613
00:43:02,360 --> 00:43:05,160
Shout three times
that "The Li is inferior to Wei,"

614
00:43:05,590 --> 00:43:07,590
and I'll let you off today.

615
00:43:07,650 --> 00:43:08,360
Pah!

616
00:43:08,670 --> 00:43:10,530
Who do you think you are, Wei Xuan?

617
00:43:10,550 --> 00:43:11,950
The Li is inferior to Wei?

618
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:14,000
More like the Wei is inferior to Xie!

619
00:43:16,920 --> 00:43:17,710
Wei Xuan!

620
00:43:23,140 --> 00:43:25,640
[Post-Credits Scene]

621
00:44:02,200 --> 00:44:09,210
[Qinwen Hall]

622
00:44:04,280 --> 00:44:05,740
F-Fan and His Lordship...

623
00:44:05,920 --> 00:44:07,110
Th-Th-They...

624
00:44:07,110 --> 00:44:07,910
What's wrong?

625
00:44:08,480 --> 00:44:09,590
Come look for yourself.

626
00:44:09,590 --> 00:44:10,550
Look, look!

627
00:44:13,440 --> 00:44:14,240
His Lordship—

628
00:44:14,320 --> 00:44:15,400
What Lordship?

629
00:44:15,400 --> 00:44:17,000
I'm still mad at him.

630
00:44:17,400 --> 00:44:20,280
One minute he's lowering his status
to be Fan's matrilocal husband,

631
00:44:20,280 --> 00:44:22,630
then he's throwing
his weight around as a marquis.

632
00:44:22,630 --> 00:44:25,230
Now he's going to marry the princess
and become a Prince Consort.

633
00:44:25,230 --> 00:44:26,190
I'm telling you,

634
00:44:26,510 --> 00:44:27,590
if he really dares

635
00:44:27,590 --> 00:44:28,710
to wrong Fan,

636
00:44:29,670 --> 00:44:30,400
I'll...

637
00:44:30,700 --> 00:44:31,340
I'll...

638
00:44:31,750 --> 00:44:32,380
I'll...

639
00:44:33,070 --> 00:44:34,400
What are you gonna do?

640
00:44:34,310 --> 00:44:37,360
[Qinwen Hall]

641
00:44:35,190 --> 00:44:36,760
I'll stay mad at him!
